text:
Hi everyone! I am having an issue with text rendering in gmail-client.
<https://yadi.sk/i/_1LdLpLc1R61UQ>
I have 2 same text blocks in one template, but gmail render them differently and I get different font-size text.
I also added
```    html { 
      -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; 
      -ms-text-size-adjust: none;
    } 
    ```
and
```&lt;meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"&gt;
&lt;meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge"&gt;
&lt;meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no"&gt;
&lt;meta name="x-apple-disable-message-reformatting"&gt;```
the text part (the second text block is the same)
```
 &lt;!-- Text Content 1--&gt;
    &lt;!--[if mso | IE]&gt;
      &lt;table
         align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="" style="width:600px;" width="600"
      &gt;
        &lt;tr&gt;
          &lt;td&gt;
      &lt;![endif]--&gt;
    &lt;div style="background:#FFFFFF;background-color:#FFFFFF;margin:0px auto;max-width:600px;"&gt;
      &lt;table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" style="background:#FFFFFF;background-color:#FFFFFF;width:100%;"&gt;
        &lt;tbody&gt;
          &lt;tr&gt;
            &lt;td style="direction:ltr;font-size:0px;padding-left:30px;padding-right:30px;padding-top:0px;padding-bottom:5px;text-align:center;"&gt;
              &lt;!--[if mso | IE]&gt;
                  &lt;table role="presentation" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"&gt;

        &lt;tr&gt;

            &lt;td
               class="" style="vertical-align:top;width:560px;"
            &gt;
          &lt;![endif]--&gt;
              &lt;div class="mj-column-per-100 mj-outlook-group-fix" style="font-size:0px;text-align:left;direction:ltr;display:inline-block;vertical-align:top;width:100%;"&gt;
                &lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" style="vertical-align:top;" width="100%"&gt;
                  &lt;tr&gt;
                    &lt;td align="left" style="font-size:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;word-break:break-word;"&gt;
                      &lt;div style="font-family:'Open Sans', 'Helvetica', 'Tahoma', sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;line-height:24px;text-align:left;color:#112336;"&gt;
                        {% widget_block rich_text 'Text_Content1' label='Text Content1' overridable=true no_wrapper=true %}
                        {% widget_attribute 'html' no_wrapper=true %}
                        {% end_widget_attribute %}
                        {% end_widget_block %}
                  		&lt;/div&gt;
                    &lt;/td&gt;
                  &lt;/tr&gt;
                &lt;/table&gt;
              &lt;/div&gt;
              &lt;!--[if mso | IE]&gt;
            &lt;/td&gt;

        &lt;/tr&gt;

                  &lt;/table&gt;
                &lt;![endif]--&gt;
            &lt;/td&gt;
          &lt;/tr&gt;
        &lt;/tbody&gt;
      &lt;/table&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;!--[if mso | IE]&gt;
          &lt;/td&gt;
        &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;/table&gt;
      &lt;![endif]--&gt;
    &lt;!-- End of Text Content 1--&gt;```
Could somebody take a look and tell me what should I add to make text the same size. Thanks in advance.
